Design Engineers
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/05 12:42:35
Ref. JB3047463
Job Description
Assist the Senior Designer with:
- Preparation of Concept drawings
- Performance Mock Up drawings if requested
- Preparation of Shop drawings
- As built drawings
- Work to the Submittal program
- Timely issue of all related documentation to programme
- Liaison between site and design as required
Skills
- Well verse in CADD Software
- Material Take-off
- Fabrication Drawings
- Show Drawings
- BIM is an advantage
Education
Bsc Engineering / BS Architecture or its equivalent
